          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Combat Sexual Harassment in Housing Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Fair Housing Act to specify that the following&nbsp;unwelcome conduct in or around a dwelling shall be considered&nbsp;sufficiently severe or pervasive as to constitute a discriminatory housing practice: (1) unwelcome touching of a sexual nature or groping; or (2) any other unwelcome conduct of a sexual nature that is intended to be coercive, threatening, or intimidating. </p>]]></text>
        </item>
